headline: Mamdani’s Rent-Freeze Agenda Sparks Slide in NYC-Linked REITs
summary: (Bloomberg) -- Shares of companies linked to New York City real estate fell Wednesday as Zohran Mamdani, a state Assembly member who has vowed to freeze rents, looks all but certain to become the Democratic nominee for mayor.Most Read from BloombergBezos Wedding Draws Protests, Soul-Searching Over Tourism in VeniceUS Renters Face Storm of Rising CostsUS State Budget Wounds Intensify From Trump, DOGE Policy ShiftsCommuters Are Caught in Johannesburg's Taxi Feuds as Transit LagsMapping the Archite
